cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.NE, cs.LG 

The paper discusses an artificial immune system approach to computer security, specifically for process anomaly detection. This falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR) and involves the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. The system also involves communication between different cell types, which could be considered a form of distributed systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the use of neural networks (cs.NE) is mentioned in the paper as a potential future direction for this research.
